!Analyze Zombie Blood
|Refugee Center Doctor
|First, you need to kill any zombie and extract the blood from its body using the blood draw kit.\nSecond, you need to deliver this blood to any working centrifuge with a computer. Equipment like this can most commonly be found at hospitals, but you can also try to search for it at medical labs.\nThird, you need to place the extracted blood on the centrifuge and analyze it using the computer nearby. If you're successful, the data will be written on an empty USB drive you have to provide.\nFinally, you need to bring the USB drive with the data back to the Doctor.
|We don't have the equipment for real analysis here so it'll need to be done in the field. I need you to get a fresh sample of zombie blood, take it to a hospital, and perform a centrifuge analysis of it.
|software_blood_data
|
