!Download Workstation Data
|Refugee Center Doctor
|
|The medical software didn't just analyze the blood, it triggered a government alert. Medical staff was under orders to immediately drive any matching samples to the nearest laboratory. That must mean the government knew! We have the destination address. Go there, get in, and bring back any records you can download off a computer.
|
