!Find Lab Tunnels
|Refugee Center Doctor
|
|In the data we found a major contract for tunneling and train equipment, ordered eight months ago. It's the best lead we have. Here's the address of the government lab where the equipment was delivered. I want you to go there, find the tunnels that they dug, and download everything you can about the train network.
