|Old Guard Representative Mission 2
|The Hell's Raiders bandit group may have an informant working inside the Refugee Center.  Investigate and bring them to justice without arousing any suspicions.
| Find the guard who looks suspicious. Ask him if he's been hiding something, then use intimidate or persuade to turn him hostile before killing him.
| Improved relationship, tutoring, or trade. 
