===Magiclysm===
Magiclysm's Forge Diviner NPC can be paid 1 Denarius to tell you the location of an interesting location. Buying their services adds a map marker. The diviner can tell you about the following:
Acid anthill, anthill, attunement altar, balrog, cave, central lab, clay deposit, demon spiders, dermatiks, dragon, Exodii, fungal bloom, fungal flowers, fungal tower, goblins, hot spring, ice lab, kraken cave, lab, magic academy, magic field, mi-go encampment, nether lab, orcs, Forge of Wonders, river, sand patch, slime pit, spider pit, spider web, strange temple, triffid grove, wizard tower, wizard tower altar. Magiclysm also adds an NPC mage that will give quests.

